data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Margate, Florida! This beautiful 3-bedroom, 1 bathroom, no HOA pool home offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and Florida living. Featuring hurricane impact windows, stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, laminate and tile flooring throughout. Oversized fenced in back yard. Roof and Water Heater replaced in 2018.Perfectly situated on a serene canal with its own walking trails giving you direct access to tranquil nature in your backyard. Centrally located, offering easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment.
